SUMMARY:Real Estate Photography  Intro and Basics
LOCATION:1630 E 7th Ave Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:For Sale! How do you photograph a house thats about to hit the
  market? Because traditional photography alone isnt enough to sell. Do you
  want to photograph real estate? Youve come to the right place. Here\, we 
 dive deep into the business of Real Estate Photography. We will talk mobil
 e homes\, fixer-uppers\, new construction\, expansive estates\, and everyt
 hing in between. How to capture marketing images that sell. Not only the g
 ear youll need\, but also the photographic techniques\, editing processes 
 and options\, business models\, the psychology of working with agents and 
 sellers\, and marketing plans to help get you business. \n\nPermalink: htt
 ps://www.tampa.gov/node/187891
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/187891
END:VEVENT
