SUMMARY:Gallery Talk: Beth Belaschky on Echos of the Luminous
LOCATION:1630 E 7th Ave Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an intimate afternoon with award-winning artist Be
 th Belaschky as she pulls back the curtain on her latest exhibition\, Echo
 s of the Luminous. In this gallery talk\, Beth will discuss her unique mul
 tidisciplinary approach\, moving far beyond the traditional photograph to 
 explore the world of holograms\, cold wax\, and light-based excavations. \
 n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187921
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/187921
END:VEVENT
