SUMMARY:2026 Hurricane Preparedness Expo
LOCATION:4810 N. Himes Ave Tampa \, FL 33614 United States
DESCRIPTION:Its time to start planning! Save the date for Tampa Fire Rescu
 es Hurricane Preparedness Expo on Saturday\, May 30\, 2026. At this event\
 , residents will have the opportunity to speak to various City of Tampa de
 partments\, community partners\, and businesses to learn how to prepare th
 eir families and homes in the event of a tropical storm or hurricane. Sand
 bags will be available\, limited to 10 per family\, while supplies last. R
 esidents interested in receiving sandbags must show a valid Drivers Licens
 e or State Identification verifying residency within the city limits. Dont
  miss out on this valuable opportunity! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.g
 ov/node/186531
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/186531
END:VEVENT
